Format raw individual concentrations table for report

nca.conc.table.Rd

Format raw individual concentrations table for report

nca.conc.table(obs, LOQ = 1e-04, sumVar = "conc", subjVar = "subjid",
  timeVar = "nom.time", omits = NULL, times = NULL,
  carryAlong = NULL, nsig = 3, bloqCode = "BLOQ")

Arguments

obs

dataset
LOQ

value of LOQ
sumVar

concentration/DV variable
subjVar

subject or id variable
timeVar

time or visit variable
omits

any subjects to be ommitted
times

nominal time
carryAlong

any variables to be carried in the table
nsig

number of significant digits
bloqCode

variable name for BLQs are flagged

Value

report ready individual concentrations table with summary statistics

  • Arguments
  • Value
